data.description: This gorgeous home is one you do not want to miss!  This elegant Lennar Stonewall Collection home has a gorgeous entry with high ceilings, wood floors and beautiful finishes. The kitchen boasts of a large island, granite countertops, and stainless appliances.  Lots of beautiful walnut-stained cabinets and prep space is in this great kitchen.  The spacious living area has soaring ceilings and beautiful corner fireplace. The lovely primary bedroom is the perfect sanctuary for relaxation.  The primary bathroom offers double sinks, soaking jetted tub and separate shower.  Game room and secondary bedrooms are upstairs.  This beautiful home offers many upgrades and amenities and is priced at a great value! Make your appointment to tour the wonderful home!
